Description: Fragment of ring foot and wall of Attic black-glazed pottery open vase (bowl?). Foot reserved, rest glazed. Incised inscription on underside.

Bernand 1970 / Le Delta égyptien d'après les textes grecs, i: les confins libyques (p. 673, no. 317)
Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (GA.1846)
